description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

Looks like Dr. Fauci won't be appearing here, after all. Mayorkas: Border plan being implemented, getting results we don't see yet. Biden bans horses on border in response to story that never happened. "Dr. Buck Fauci" does impersonation of Fauci turning down interview with us. JD Vance on why he's running for senate. How did all those Haitians get to the border?
